  "title": "Waffles Placeable Foods",
  "description": "A few new animated foods, each can be placed if crouching. Foods can be eaten in-hand or while placed, like cake.\n\nSome foods give fun status effects!",
  "body": "This mod adds around 20 new foods (and counting). Most of these have stages of consumption, like a vanilla cake. They can each be placed while crouching (in any direction, even upside down) and eaten like a cake, or simply eaten normally. Some even give you fun status effects.\nCare has been taken to balance their crafting recipes and hunger values with vanilla food in version 1.5+.\nTo find crafting recipes, I recommend installing Just Enough Items (or similar).\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/kALDdVOI/images/8a25efe86ef415e56b27300fe638af48003058a1.png\" alt=\"Bacon and eggs\" width=\"150\"/>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/kALDdVOI/images/83978a64ec50ae9f961f635af56eb3ea97187431.gif\" alt=\"Bacon and eggs\" width=\"150\"/>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/kALDdVOI/images/dcce3466bbd379dbf2eb206380f27fe20b684032.gif\" alt=\"Bacon and eggs\" width=\"150\"/>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/kALDdVOI/images/e9e758514d8587484c2b5b2506d923f3712b7b1d.gif\" alt=\"Chocolate\" width=\"150\"/>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/kALDdVOI/images/e75ab4b0fc2c9d61e2300a89c89f3fe85aa88f83.gif\" alt=\"Pancakes\" width=\"150\"/>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/kALDdVOI/images/74f0f77ef2e17b0b6983f5d5c37f3b97a7402589.gif\" alt=\"Hot chocolate\" width=\"150\"/>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/kALDdVOI/images/51449b63fb01697d7bc3269bb25ac8eac57d59f5.png\" alt=\"Strawberry pocky\" width=\"150\"/>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/kALDdVOI/images/1f5212940532aa066974e5307f46c417bab7677b.png\" alt=\"Hamburger\" width=\"150\"/>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/kALDdVOI/images/29c308c3e4b9f98aa6b7afd8d2d90d02eabe720d.png\" alt=\"Heart\" width=\"150\"/>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/kALDdVOI/images/4db7ba70fc5a555803570e88fca1d787c57d2e1b.png\" alt=\"Cookies\" width=\"150\"/>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/kALDdVOI/images/58a8338c2febcc65b2344016f23446cd13776e77.png\" alt=\"Cake\" width=\"150\"/>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/kALDdVOI/images/58de9339a4c1f2345ec300fcf754727a7d654b07.png\" alt=\"Pizza\" width=\"150\"/>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/kALDdVOI/images/5fc7fe7807ea78bf91e8545dcd48a9e99598b89d.png\" alt=\"Banana split\" width=\"150\"/>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/kALDdVOI/images/8d2286010ca4fe2ab8c5c240a60136b25b5de543.png\" alt=\"Marshmallows\" width=\"150\"/>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/kALDdVOI/images/936ce1c873cfbaa49f101a9f407a68115db40036.png\" alt=\"Chocolate pocky\" width=\"150\"/>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/kALDdVOI/images/9983704f1b337fc649caf7401835eb6749fc993c.png\" alt=\"Coffee\" width=\"150\"/>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/kALDdVOI/images/d9e47151a612e5238f6561f4cb875d915ced9adc.png\" alt=\"Waffle\" width=\"150\"/>\n\nMore foods in-game! (I cannot be bothered screenshotting them all)\n\n- DEPENDENCIES\n- \n- Fabric: Fabric API\n- \n- Forge/NeoForge (combined Fabric versions only): Sinytra Connector, Forgified Fabric API\n- (Otherwise no dependencies)\n\n## Check out my other mods!\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/4QoWk5WV/4ff9e6f1cb16d13959893a1526ce55fab682a57d.gif\" alt=\"Waffles Moss\" width=\"150\"/>\n\n[Waffle's Moss](https://modrinth.com/mod/waffles-moss)\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/I7mv6L5j/0028b8d9a1fd93571b6a3a415cc69ad38970ce09.gif\" alt=\"Waffles Terracotta Plaster\" width=\"150\"/>\n\n[Waffle's Terracotta Plaster](https://modrinth.com/mod/waffles-terracotta-plaster)\n",
